Author: Marjorie521
Title: LAMONEDA: THE BIGGEST BOUNTY CAMPAIGN EVER!!
Body: https://i.imgur.com/tp7Y4Zo.jpg https://i.imgur.com/b1zT8QP.png _______________________________________________________________________________   __________________________________________________________________________ LAMONEDA Revolutionizing the event ticketing industry, bringing artist, promoters and event organizers closer to their fans.. _______________________________________________________________________________   __________________________________________________________________________  https://i.imgur.com/V3tVSU9.png https://i.imgur.com/t7vBbJf.png https://i.imgur.com/nK7Vo1R.png https://i.imgur.com/DqpmUM0.png   ANN | WEBSITE | WHITEPAPER | TELEGRAM | EXPLAINER VIDEO  Welcome to LAMONEDA Bounty Program   We are building up a Decentralized Smart Ticketing network that will revolutionize the event ticketing industry, bringing artist, promoters and event organizers closer to their fans. We’re growing our LAMONEDA community now! Please join our bounty programs to help us spread out our goals and future plans. You can help us by talking about LAMONEDA on social media; writing/sharing our articles on your websites/blogs. You’ll earn LAMONEDA tokens in return.  By completing bounty tasks, you will receive bounty divided into the following categories: twitter, Facebook, writing blog posts on personal channel and posting articles in popular media.  At the end of pre-sale, we will distribute in total ……LAMONEDA Tokens Please remember that only for Social Media article, Blog, Media, and Video will earn you LMDA  Tokens guaranteed, so independent of any stake campaigns.  The bounty budget is divided into the following categories:  •   Twitter Campaign •   Facebook Campaign •   Blog articles       •   Media publications   •   Video Campaign •   BTT Translation Campaign •   Reddit Campaign    1.   Twitter Campaign  Follow LAMONEDA Twitter and earn: 100 LMDA Token  Multiple accounts registration is not allowed. One person=one account. All related accounts will be deleted. We will check the following status before and after the ICO.  The total amount of LMDAdistributed in this category is 700kLMDA.  Please us this form to enroll yourself   2.   Facebook Campaign  Like LAMONEDA Facebook and earn: 50 LMDA  Multiple accounts registration is not allowed. One person=one account. All related accounts will be deleted.  The total amount of stakes distributed in this category is 700k LMDA.  Please us this form to enroll yourself  3.   Write a post on your personal channel/social media about LAMONEDA {LMDA Tokens}  Write any post or articles about LAMONEDA in any language on your own blogsor your social net personal page, for example, Facebook or LinkedIn page. We will check and state them and award from 500 – 2000 Tokens.  The article should be available on the Internet. To rate your article, we will check the popularity of your blog and the quality of the content.  •   The content must be unique, not copied and pasted from elsewhere •   The article mustbe written in English, contain only unique content andpublicly accessible •   The article mustbe 500 characters or more (without spaces) in length •   The article mustcontain at least 2 links to LAMONEDA website or related content(Twitter, Facebook, Telegram, Reddit, BTT etc) •   We don’t allow websites with no audience or new websites; the website youchoose to publish your text must be at least 2 months old and must haveuser activity •   We will evaluate blogs according to their quality in order to reward thoseparticipants who invested the greatest effort in their posts •   Bounties will beawarded according to the above 6 quality levels •   Please disclaim the article “Sponsored Post”  It can be your blog or your social net personal page, for example, Facebook or LinkedIn page. The article should be available on the Internet. To class your article, we will check the popularity of your blog and the quality of the content. The total amount of LAMONEDA tokensdistributed in this category is 1 Million LMDA   Please us this form to enroll yourself  4.   Media/Journalists Publication  If you are a big media or a trendsetter, please check this bounty. You can help us to post your articles on big and popular websites/media. E.g., you can write an article about LAMONEDA in Forbes, Coindesk, Coin speaker, Investing or any other well-known financial or cryptocurrency related media.  The article should be available on the Internet. To class your article, we will check the popularity of the media and the quality of the content.  You will be awarded below scores according to the quality/traffic/popularity of your article and the media:  Qualified:   Awarded ……. 5k Good:      Awarded … 8k Nice:       Awarded ……10k Excellent:   Awarded…….20k  •   The content must be unique, not copied and pasted from elsewhere •   The article mustbe written in English or your native language, contain only unique content andpublicly accessible •   The article mustbe 600 characters or more (without spaces) in length •   The article must contain at least 2 links to LAMONEDA website or related content(Twitter, Facebook, Telegram, Reddit, BTT etc) •   We don’t allow websites with no audience or new websites; the website youchoose to publish your text must be at least 2 months old and must haveuser activity •   We will evaluate blogs according to their quality in order to reward thoseparticipants who invested the greatest effort in their posts •   Bounties will beawarded according to the above 6 quality levels •   Please disclaim the article “Sponsored Post”  The total amount of LMDAdistributed in this category is 1.6 Million LAMONEDA   Please us this form to enroll yourself  5.   Video Campaign  If you are a vlogger specialized in cryptocurrency filed, please feel free to join us and get the tokens. You can produce a video requested as follows:  •   You must produce at least 3-minute video •   Your YouTube channel subscribers must be more than 100 •   Video must be publicly accessible •   Your title must include the word LAMONEDA •   Please include “Sponsored Video” for the title •   Produce quality video explaining benefits of LAMONEDA Features of LAMONEDA, and guides to LMDA •   You must have at least 30 views before being accepted •   The video should talk about the LAMONEDA project positively. We will evaluate videos according to their quality in order to reward those participants who invested the greatest effort in their posts. •   Bounties will be awardedaccording to the above quality levels:  Qualified:   Awarded 1000 LMDA Good:      Awarded 2000LMDA Nice:       Awarded 3000LMDA Excellent:   Awarded 5000LMDA  The total amount of LMDAdistributed in this category is 1 Million LMDA   Please us this form to enroll yourself   6.   RedditCampaign  You must join our Reddit channel https://www.reddit.com/user/Lamoneda/to be eligible. Your Reddit account should be at least 1 month old and have at least 2 posts and 20 karmas. You must make at least 5 Comments/posts about Legolas Exchange in a week.  Posts must to be made on one of the following subreddits:  https://www.reddit.com/r/ethereumnoobies/ https://www.reddit.com/r/ethtrader https://www.reddit.com/r/icocrypto https://www.reddit.com/r/cryptocurrency  Spam posts and comments with negative Karma will not be accepted.  Payment 100 LMDA per post/comment Maximum 10 per week) Total Participant required 50  You must report your activities in this threadhttps://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4396733.new#new every week in the following format to get payment  Your BitcointalkUsername : Your Profile : Reddit Username : Reddit Profile : ETH Address: The total amount of LMDAdistributed in this category is 500k LMDA   Please us this form to enroll yourself  7.   BTT Translation Campaign {Stakes}  We are happy to offer a translation reward for those who help us for Whitepaper, ANN, Bounty thread translationThe following languagesare welcome: Japanese, (Simplified and Traditional), German, French, Spanish, Italian,Russian, Dutch Arabic and Hindi.  •   To join, you need to be at least a Jr Member. •   Each member should translate the official LAMONEDA BTT Thread post, whitepaper, and original thread ANNs. Youneed to create your local thread at Bitcointalk to get the reward. •   You need to keep the format, words, documents, and images of the translated stuff the same as original official threads of LAMONEDA. Any incomplete or unqualified translations will not be counted.  The total amount of LAMONEDA distributed in this category is 500kLMDA  Rewards are stated below:  •   Whitepaper translation: 2000 LMDA •   ANNs translation: 2000LMDA   Please us this form to enroll yourself    Within one month after the ICO ends, your final number of tokens will be calculated and deposited to your Ethereum registered wallet. Here is an email you have any questions regarding the bounty campaign or if you need assistance, join our Telegram channel here: or more information!  ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMER  •   To prevent fraud and theft, the wallet address provided during signup cannot bechanged for any reason. •   We reserve the right to remove from any campaign user spamming, cheating orusing multi-accounts. Negative trust are not allowed to join this campaign,negative trust received during the campaign will result in permanent banningfrom any campaign and all stakes will be deleted. •   We reserve the right to remove any user from any campaign if there is a suspect of their dishonesty: we will not give any explanation. •   Users may not be accepted in the campaign for any reasons. •   We reserve the right to change, modify, add or remove portions of these terms andconditions at any time without prior notice and you accept and agree to thechanges. It is your responsibility to check these Terms periodically for changes.
